{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had jewelry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had necklaces and et cetera, which was hidden in pockets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they have all kind of different thing, what basically we were not allowed to touch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was something what they had a box for smaller jewelry, another one for bigger one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to pile the clothes and suitcases, shoes, everything separate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on the-- on-- continuously under SS guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That you have to understand, when we left camp to the railroad station, we were strip searched, That nothing should come out of the camp, come back to camp, once again, strip searched.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That nothing can come from the radio station, back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why we couldn't manipulate, we couldn't organize anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always, the same SS guard who took us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a 12-hour shift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The shift was we had to be at the station at 7:00.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stayed till 7:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was always with my brother, by the way, together, always on a day shift while we did this work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we found out the whole operation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw-- I had the unpleasant thing of seeing Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mengele every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Suddenly we knew when we saw the big chimneys, and we know the chimneys is basically, that-- that-- the-- the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we saw where the gas chamber is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And also what we have seen, where the smell comes from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The smell came that even with the tremendous German precision-- while they were precise in everything, what they did, they did not calculate it properly, that it took somewhere in around 40 minutes to burn the bodies.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the gas chamber took 10 to 11 minutes, to kill the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
